", "name": "Fox Sex Farm", "steam_appid": 3122920, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/4830c99f1276b7950ef585df676efc3b.poster.avif?t=1776827274\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/4830c99f1276b7950ef585df676efc3b.webm?t=1776827274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/4830c99f1276b7950ef585df676efc3b.mp4?t=1776827274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You've come to a remote area far from the city with the intention of living in seclusion.<br>You stumble upon an abandoned house and decide to move in.<br>Suddenly, cries for help are heard from outside the house, and in that moment, your happy future begins to change.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Icasia (CV：Ayane Mako)</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/912c9dfd8a776566c52e1c6fa89c61e0.avif?t=1776827274\" width=614 height=345 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feifei (CV：Enokizu Mao)</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/da81b6aef0507d3a2372bc4f7f8329c1.avif?t=1776827274\" width=614 height=345 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Liz (CV：Misonoo Mei)</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/161bd0dbbd79dc06c5b619d3e8f6b327.avif?t=1776827274\" width=614 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Attiya (CV：Wataame Tabeko)</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/5a35db6fc21e638409f0001599168190.avif?t=1776827274\" width=614 height=345 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Notiz (CV：Hiiragi Nana)</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/b05efe2562c18e270b7bee36d01b3fc4.avif?t=1776827274\" width=614 height=345 /></span><br><br>The game is an economic simulation.<br>You must acquire resources through farming, logging, mining and other activities to develop your residence, <br><br>and build relationships with the 5 main characters to add fun to your life and help you in your work.<br>Take care of their material needs, including sleep and food.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/2630ea7ff715a4d00d0e718a3139f669.poster.avif?t=1776827274\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/2630ea7ff715a4d00d0e718a3139f669.webm?t=1776827274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/2630ea7ff715a4d00d0e718a3139f669.mp4?t=1776827274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And develop technology to get more types of resources.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/c990ae705dbe1bf54b2bb48c20851c61.avif?t=1776827274\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><br><br>You'll build a variety of automated facilities to speed up your resource gathering.<br>Plan your circuits to connect the high-tech equipment so everything works smoothly.<br>And catch some rabbits.<br>Put them to work on your facilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/6106c8968b8ade38c1438adf49cd6b94.avif?t=1776827274\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><br><br>As well as fending off the invading swarms of bugs, you'll also have to face off against powerful creatures to survive in this unfamiliar environment.<br>Craft better weapons and build a line of defence.<br>Let the bullets from your gun tear through their shells.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/ffc17a1816b46ff52fbbad2e54665423.avif?t=1776827274\" width=1560 height=878 /></span>", "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/4830c99f1276b7950ef585df676efc3b.poster.avif?t=1776827274\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/4830c99f1276b7950ef585df676efc3b.webm?t=1776827274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/4830c99f1276b7950ef585df676efc3b.mp4?t=1776827274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You've come to a remote area far from the city with the intention of living in seclusion.<br>You stumble upon an abandoned house and decide to move in.<br>Suddenly, cries for help are heard from outside the house, and in that moment, your happy future begins to change.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Icasia (CV：Ayane Mako)</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/912c9dfd8a776566c52e1c6fa89c61e0.avif?t=1776827274\" width=614 height=345 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feifei (CV：Enokizu Mao)</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122920/extras/da81b6aef0507d3a2372bc4f7f8329c1.avif?t=17768272